{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Decouple electricity prices from gas prices ",
        "additional_details": "The United Kingdom has the one of the highest electricity prices in Europe. By simply decoupling our gas price from electricity, we believe this could bring everyone's bill's down.",
        "background": "This government should decouple our gas price from electricity. It has been reported that this alone could cut bills by \u00a3200.",
